  "html_content": "<style>.tg{font-family:monospace;padding:20px 24px;background:#0f172a;color:#e2e8f0}.map{display:flex;gap:0;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:16px}.sw{flex:1}.hw{flex:1.5}.mid{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;padding:40px 10px 0}.panel-lbl{font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:center}.sw .panel-lbl{color:#3b82f6}.hw .panel-lbl{color:#a855f7}.outer{border:1px dashed #1e293b;border-radius:8px;padding:8px;background:#080d18}.grid-note{font-size:9px;color:#475569;margin-bottom:6px}.sw-blk{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;border:1px solid #2563eb;border-radius:4px;padding:5px 8px;margin-bottom:5px;background:#1e3a5f18;font-size:11px;color:#93c5fd}.dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#3b82f6;flex-shrink:0}.blk-note{color:#475569;font-size:9px}.sw-cap{font-size:9px;color:#f59e0b;margin-top:6px;border-top:1px solid #1e293b;padding-top:6px}.sm{border:1px solid #7e22ce;border-radius:6px;padding:6px 8px;margin-bottom:6px}.sm-ttl{font-size:10px;color:#c084fc;margin-bottom:5px}.warp{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;margin-bottom:3px}.wlbl{font-size:9px;color:#64748b;width:44px;flex-shrink:0}.wline{display:flex;gap:1px}.wt{width:5px;height:14px;border-radius:1px;background:#14532d;border:1px solid #22c55e}.wnote{font-size:9px;color:#475569;align-self:center;margin-left:3px}.sm-more{font-size:9px;color:#334155;margin-top:3px}.hw-cap{font-size:9px;color:#f59e0b;margin-top:6px;border-top:1px solid #1e293b;padding-top:6px}.sched{font-size:9px;color:#64748b;text-align:center;line-height:1.6}.arr{font-size:20px;color:#334155;margin-top:4px}.fbar{background:#1e293b;border:1px solid #334155;border-radius:6px;padding:10px 14px;font-size:11px;line-height:2.1}.kw{color:#818cf8}.val{color:#34d399;font-weight:700}.eq{color:#f59e0b}.dim{color:#64748b}</style><div class='tg'><div class='map'><div class='sw'><div class='panel-lbl'>CUDA Software</div><div class='outer'><div class='grid-note'>Grid</div><div class='sw-blk'><div class='dot'></div>Block 0<span class='blk-note'>&nbsp;256 threads</span></div><div class='sw-blk'><div class='dot'></div>Block 1<span class='blk-note'>&nbsp;256 threads</span></div><div class='sw-blk'><div class='dot'></div>Block 2<span class='blk-note'>&nbsp;256 threads</span></div><div class='sw-blk'><div class='dot'></div>Block 3<span class='blk-note'>&nbsp;256 threads</span></div><div class='sw-cap'>&#9432; max 1024 threads/block — hard limit, không thể khai báo block lớn hơn</div></div></div><div class='mid'><div class='sched'>GPU<br>scheduler<br>assigns</div><div class='arr'>&#8594;</div></div><div class='hw'><div class='panel-lbl'>GPU Hardware — Streaming Multiprocessors</div><div class='outer'><div class='sm'><div class='sm-ttl'>Streaming Multiprocessor 0 &#8592; Block 0, Block 2</div><div class='warp'><span class='wlbl'>Warp 0</span><div class='wline'><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div></div><span class='wnote'>t 0&#8211;31</span></div><div class='warp'><span class='wlbl'>Warp 1</span><div class='wline'><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div></div><span class='wnote'>t 32&#8211;63</span></div><div class='sm-more'>&#183;&#183;&#183; 6 more warps (256 &#247; 32 = 8 warps/block)</div></div><div class='sm'><div class='sm-ttl'>Streaming Multiprocessor 1 &#8592; Block 1, Block 3</div><div class='warp'><span class='wlbl'>Warp 0</span><div class='wline'><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div><div class='wt'></div></div><span class='wnote'>t 0&#8211;31</span></div><div class='sm-more'>&#183;&#183;&#183; 7 more warps</div></div><div class='hw-cap'>&#9432; 1536 threads/SM = giới hạn concurrency (occupancy)<br>&#8226; 256 threads/block &#8594; 6 blocks <b>thường trú</b> cùng lúc (100%)<br>&#8226; 1024 threads/block &#8594; 1 block thường trú (67%)<br><span style='color:#64748b'>thường trú (resident) &#8800; chạy cùng 1 khoảnh khắc &#8212; xem Warp Scheduler &#8595;</span></div></div></div></div><div class='fbar'><div><span class='val'>256</span><span class='dim'> threads/block &#247; </span><span class='val'>32</span><span class='dim'> = </span><span class='val'>8 warps</span><span class='dim'> chạy trên SM</span></div><div><span class='kw'>threadIdx.x / 32</span><span class='eq'> &#8594; </span><span class='dim'>warp index &nbsp;|&nbsp; </span><span class='kw'>threadIdx.x % 32</span><span class='eq'> &#8594; </span><span class='dim'>lane (vị trí trong warp)</span></div></div><style>.pw{margin-top:18px;border-top:1px solid #1e293b;padding-top:16px}.pw-h{font-size:13px;color:#38bdf8;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px}.pw-sub{font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:12px}.pw-sub b{color:#e2e8f0}.pw-ex{font-size:11px;color:#cbd5e1;margin-bottom:8px}.pw-ex b{color:#38bdf8}.pw-warps{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(8,1fr);gap:6px;margin-bottom:16px}.pw-chip{background:#0b1220;border:1px solid #1e293b;border-radius:6px;padding:6px 4px;text-align:center}.pw-wlab{font-family:monospace;font-size:10px;color:#64748b;margin-bottom:4px}.pw-wlab.pw-warn{color:#fbbf24}.pw-bar{height:26px;background:#1e293b;border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden;display:flex;align-items:flex-end}.pw-fill{background:#16a34a;height:100%;border-right:1px solid #22c55e}.pw-cnt{font-family:monospace;font-size:10px;color:#4ade80;margin-top:4px}.pw-cnt.pw-warn{color:#fbbf24}.pw-zlbl{font-size:11px;color:#cbd5e1;margin-bottom:6px}.pw-zlbl b{color:#fbbf24}.pw-zoom{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(32,1fr);gap:2px;margin-bottom:4px}.pw-l{height:22px;border-radius:2px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:9px}.pw-on{background:#16a34a;border:1px solid #22c55e}.pw-off{background:repeating-linear-gradient(45deg,#334155,#334155 3px,#0b1220 3px,#0b1220 6px);border:1px dashed #64748b;color:#94a3b8}.pw-zkey{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:9px;color:#64748b;margin-bottom:2px}.pw-note{font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.8;margin-top:12px;background:#0b1220;border:1px solid #1e293b;border-radius:6px;padding:10px 12px}.pw-note b{color:#e2e8f0}.pw-note .no{color:#f87171}.pw-note .ok{color:#4ade80}</style><div class='pw'><div class='pw-h'>&#9635; Warp = 32 lane cố định &#8212; block chia hết 32 hay không?</div><div class='pw-sub'>Warp <b>luôn luôn 32 thread</b> (warpSize = 32, cứng trong phần cứng, không co giãn). Số warp = <b>ceil(threads / 32)</b> &#8212; làm tròn <b>LÊN</b>. Nên block không chia hết 32 sẽ có 1 warp lẻ.</div><div class='pw-ex'>Ví dụ: block <b>248 threads</b> &#8594; ceil(248 / 32) = <b>8 warp</b> (KHÔNG phải mỗi warp 31 thread):</div><div class='pw-warps'><div class='pw-chip'><div class='pw-wlab'>W0</div><div class='pw-bar'><div class='pw-fill' style='width:100%'></div></div><div class='pw-cnt'>32</div></div><div class='pw-chip'><div class='pw-wlab'>W1</div><div class='pw-bar'><div class='pw-fill' style='width:100%'></div></div><div class='pw-cnt'>32</div></div><div class='pw-chip'><div class='pw-wlab'>W2</div><div class='pw-bar'><div class='pw-fill' style='width:100%'></div></div><div class='pw-cnt'>32</div></div><div class='pw-chip'><div class='pw-wlab'>W3</div><div class='pw-bar'><div class='pw-fill' style='width:100%'></div></div><div class='pw-cnt'>32</div></div><div class='pw-chip'><div class='pw-wlab'>W4</div><div class='pw-bar'><div class='pw-fill' style='width:100%'></div></div><div class='pw-cnt'>32</div></div><div class='pw-chip'><div class='pw-wlab'>W5</div><div class='pw-bar'><div class='pw-fill' style='width:100%'></div></div><div class='pw-cnt'>32</div></div><div class='pw-chip'><div class='pw-wlab'>W6</div><div class='pw-bar'><div class='pw-fill' style='width:100%'></div></div><div class='pw-cnt'>32</div></div><div class='pw-chip'><div class='pw-wlab pw-warn'>W7</div><div class='pw-bar'><div class='pw-fill' style='width:75%'></div></div><div class='pw-cnt pw-warn'>24</div></div></div><div class='pw-zlbl'>Warp 7 (phóng to): <b>24 lane chạy + 8 lane chết</b></div><div class='pw-zoom'><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-on'></div><div class='pw-l pw-off'>&#215;</div><div class='pw-l pw-off'>&#215;</div><div class='pw-l pw-off'>&#215;</div><div class='pw-l pw-off'>&#215;</div><div class='pw-l pw-off'>&#215;</div><div class='pw-l pw-off'>&#215;</div><div class='pw-l pw-off'>&#215;</div><div class='pw-l pw-off'>&#215;</div></div><div class='pw-zkey'><span>lane 0&#8211;23 = thread 224&#8211;247 (active)</span><span>lane 24&#8211;31 = inactive (masked)</span></div><div class='pw-note'>&#8226; Warp 7 vẫn chiếm <b>1 slot warp đầy đủ</b>; 8 lane chết vẫn chạy lockstep cùng warp nhưng bị che (masked) &#8594; kết quả bị vứt &#8594; <b>phí 25%</b> warp đó.<br>&#8226; Block 248 tốn <b>y hệt 8 warp</b> như block 256 &#8212; chọn 248 chỉ toàn thiệt.<br>&#8226; &#8658; Luôn chọn block size <b>bội số của 32</b> (128 / 256 / 512 / 1024) để <span class='ok'>không phí lane</span>.<br>&#8226; Khác với guard <b>if (i &lt; n) return;</b> (xử lý khi <b>grid</b> dư thread so với dữ liệu) &#8212; lane chết ở đây là do <b>block</b> không chia hết 32. Hai tầng khác nhau.</div></div><style>.sc{margin-top:18px;border-top:1px solid #1e293b;padding-top:16px}.sc-h{font-size:13px;color:#c084fc;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px}.sc-sub{font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:10px}.sc-sub b{color:#e2e8f0}.sc-leg{display:flex;gap:16px;font-size:10px;color:#64748b;margin-bottom:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}.sc-leg span{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}.sc-key{width:14px;height:14px;border-radius:3px;display:inline-block;flex-shrink:0}.sc-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:104px repeat(7,minmax(0,1fr));gap:3px;font-size:10px}.sc-ch{text-align:center;color:#64748b;padding:3px 0;font-family:monospace}.sc-ch.sc-now{color:#0f172a;background:#f59e0b;border-radius:4px;font-weight:700}.sc-rl{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;color:#cbd5e1;font-family:monospace;padding-left:8px;border-left:3px solid #334155}.sc-rl .sc-sm{color:#475569;font-size:9px}.sc-g0{border-left-color:#3b82f6}.sc-g1{border-left-color:#a855f7}.sc-g2{border-left-color:#14b8a6}.sc-g3{border-left-color:#ec4899}.sc-cell{height:20px;border-radius:3px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:9px}.sc-w{background:#0b1220;border:1px solid #1e293b;color:#334155}.sc-i{background:#16a34a;border:1px solid #22c55e;color:#dcfce7;font-weight:700}.sc-s{background:repeating-linear-gradient(45deg,#78350f,#78350f 4px,#0b1220 4px,#0b1220 8px);border:1px dashed #f59e0b;color:#fbbf24}.sc-nc{box-shadow:0 0 0 2px #f59e0b}.sc-note{font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.8;margin-top:12px;background:#0b1220;border:1px solid #1e293b;border-radius:6px;padding:10px 12px}.sc-note b{color:#e2e8f0}.sc-note .ok{color:#4ade80}.sc-note .no{color:#f87171}</style><div class='sc'><div class='sc-h'>&#9654; Warp Scheduler &#8212; thực thi theo từng chu kỳ clock</div><div class='sc-sub'>SM có <b>4 warp scheduler</b>. Mỗi chu kỳ, mỗi scheduler phát lệnh cho <b>1 warp sẵn sàng</b> &#8594; tối đa <b>~4 warp / chu kỳ</b>. Các warp còn lại vẫn thường trú, chờ tới lượt.</div><div class='sc-leg'><span><span class='sc-key' style='background:#16a34a;border:1px solid #22c55e'></span>&#9654; chạy (issue)</span><span><span class='sc-key' style='background:#0b1220;border:1px solid #1e293b'></span>chờ (ready)</span><span><span class='sc-key' style='background:repeating-linear-gradient(45deg,#78350f,#78350f 4px,#0b1220 4px,#0b1220 8px);border:1px dashed #f59e0b'></span>đợi memory (stall)</span></div><div class='sc-grid'><div></div><div class='sc-ch'>t0</div><div class='sc-ch'>t1</div><div class='sc-ch sc-now'>t2</div><div class='sc-ch'>t3</div><div class='sc-ch'>t4</div><div class='sc-ch'>t5</div><div class='sc-ch'>t6</div><div class='sc-rl sc-g0'>W0<span class='sc-sm'>&#183; sched0</span></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i sc-nc'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-rl sc-g0'>W1<span class='sc-sm'>&#183; sched0</span></div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w sc-nc'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-rl sc-g1'>W2<span class='sc-sm'>&#183; sched1</span></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i sc-nc'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-rl sc-g1'>W3<span class='sc-sm'>&#183; sched1</span></div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-s sc-nc'>mem</div><div class='sc-cell sc-s'>mem</div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-rl sc-g2'>W4<span class='sc-sm'>&#183; sched2</span></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i sc-nc'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-rl sc-g2'>W5<span class='sc-sm'>&#183; sched2</span></div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w sc-nc'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-rl sc-g3'>W6<span class='sc-sm'>&#183; sched3</span></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i sc-nc'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-rl sc-g3'>W7<span class='sc-sm'>&#183; sched3</span></div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w sc-nc'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div><div class='sc-cell sc-i'>&#9654;</div><div class='sc-cell sc-w'></div></div><div class='sc-note'><b>Đọc theo cột (mỗi cột = 1 chu kỳ clock):</b> cột vàng <b>t2</b> có đúng <b>4 warp &#9654; chạy</b> (1 warp mỗi scheduler) &#8212; không phải cả block.<br>&#8226; 1 block = 256 threads = <b>8 warp</b> &#8594; cần <b>&#8805; 2 chu kỳ</b> mới phát lệnh cho cả 8 warp một lượt &#8594; <span class='no'>KHÔNG</span> “cả block trong 1 chu kỳ”.<br>&#8226; <b>W3 đợi memory</b> ở t2&#8211;t3 (ô sọc “mem”) &#8594; scheduler bỏ qua, chạy warp khác &#8594; SM không ngồi rảnh = <b>latency hiding</b>.<br>&#8226; Có 6 block = <b>48 warp thường trú</b> &#8594; càng nhiều warp “dự bị”, scheduler càng dễ lấp đủ 4 slot mỗi chu kỳ &#8594; đó là lý do <b>occupancy cao</b> chạy nhanh hơn.<br>&#8226; Trong <b>1 warp</b>: cả 32 thread chạy <span class='ok'>song song thật sự</span> (SIMT). Giữa các warp: <b>luân phiên</b> theo chu kỳ.</div></div></div>"
}